    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and minor tears in the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it at its best. It's a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
